Scottish Independent Schools are dedicated to providing a learning environment that will prepare children and encourage them with the skills necessary to succeed, whatever the future may be.
It cannot be denied at this time, in a global business environment, that languages continue to be vital for the future of the country, so it must be reflected in education.
